{"tid":786865,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇結婚唔擺酒？","createTime":"2018-08-20T08:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T09:58:24.000Z","uid":10630,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3f9e92db1f61979346fc5ddf9d0597ecb777dced","tid":786865,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"係連食餐飯都無個隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多係簽紙個陣叫d比較親既親朋戚友<br />\n<br />\n自己就幾鐘意呢d 簡簡單單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔需要用一大筆錢去做一晚既大龍鳳<br />\n影下結婚相 同另一半去下旅行 <br />\n<br />\n同屋企人簡單咁討論過 死都話要擺酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話唔擺酒 好似無人知你結左婚<br />\n好無面之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直都覺得結婚係2個人既事 2個鐘意點咪點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解一定要跟傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 簡簡單單就好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定要擺酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f03656348d5fad9a0c3667735b1c151151ff35f","tid":786865,"uid":195030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:53:03.000Z","msg":"有啲傳統係擺左酒先算係結婚，齋註冊唔算，不過傳統呢家野聽下咪算，咁緊張做咩"},{"pid":"5edb6b9a1c78fa56962939df866064a969ba218a","tid":786865,"uid":30794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"自己同伴侶鍾意咪得囉 依家叫你同其他人一齊結咩"},{"pid":"1b6b3e5b458988efc7b096ce8e989449253d5569","tid":786865,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:56:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5da71e954456fe84927c1ee34181316a5a492b49","tid":786865,"uid":130586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"唔擺酒都要食餐飯同派餅卡<br />\n<br />\n以前同樓主一樣想乜都唔整唔搞<br />\n俾老母屌咗一大輪<br />\n話唔可以唔出聲就結<br />\n唔係以後見到親戚 對方問點解結婚唔請我去飲時解釋唔到喎<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔多關我事 我都唔怕人問<br />\n但諗落結婚係兩個家庭嘅事<br />\n食餐飯派餅卡咁小事咪順吓佢意<br />\n反正唔使擺酒搞婚禮已經煩少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c62707e73cbe91b6df725c1a6c9dc57829fb43","tid":786865,"uid":25560,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"堅持要擺酒個d叫佢全資付出,<br />\n唔係就shut up"},{"pid":"f918c716ae4fd46235b0434b0248471fdfa9019c","tid":786865,"uid":180922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:59:24.000Z","msg":"除左長輩之外，身邊朋友/同事都嘈你做咩唔擺<br />\n又話你一定後悔乜乜乜，大有大搞 細有細搞<br />\n煩到仆街"},{"pid":"71430148f7a941e715fca9a2234838f3ab023352","tid":786865,"uid":26066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:00:47.000Z","msg":"老一輩嗰啲都係想喺班親朋戚友面前威返次，坐一次主家席，冇辦法"},{"pid":"b15386910117472e6e584cf42512c32f0bc166c4","tid":786865,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:06:38.000Z","msg":"有得你唔擺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男人緊係唔想擺架啦<br />\n但女人個個都唔會唔想擺"},{"pid":"95ba9141191a82611b3a0c179279e82618dc1a0d","tid":786865,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"最好婚都唔洗結TIM<br />\n一齊同居咪算囉"},{"pid":"2554e4447dfcd55861b06df3441627a71c0d2ccc","tid":786865,"uid":150053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女家屋企人一定係覺得, 你娶我個女唔擺酒貼埋大床咁"}]}